  LABEL "aaron@ardiri.com" AUTOID AT (54 PrevTop+11) FONT 1
  LABEL "PilRC" AUTOID AT (15 PrevTop+8)

  FORMBITMAP AT (88 PrevTop+14) BITMAP bitmapPalm

  LABEL "Copyright 2000" AUTOID AT (8 PrevTop+10)
