  LABEL "http://www.ardiri.com/" AUTOID AT (CENTER PrevTop+15) FONT 1
  LABEL "Copyright 2000" AUTOID AT (8 PrevTop+20)
  FORMBITMAP AT (88 PrevTop) BITMAP bitmapPalm

  LABEL "Aaron Ardiri" AUTOID AT (8 PrevTop+12)
