  LABEL "PilRC demo" AUTOID AT (8 PrevTop+20) FONT 1
  LABEL "version 0.1beta" AUTOID AT (8 PrevTop+12) FONT 1

  BUTTON "Ok" ID deviFormOkButton AT (CENTER 136 40 AUTO)
END

FORM ID mainForm AT (0 0 160 160) NOSAVEBEHIND
